ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a8e636db3b994e713050ea3575634c6d7be3c0","tid":1537432,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少碰中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"7c96fb9871d2ae68cd63338fd1fda6669e09a7aa","tid":1537432,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9c3139462e46ec3c101128f45349c336328c213","tid":1537432,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"fd1ba542986c05e3dfe87edd192a8c6d44daf4c8","tid":1537432,"uid":122518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"6cb9b5836e74ff3fe741639452718770b5019e0d","tid":1537432,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:53:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"436148e9123e47d0cf191630cf30ae8a2d49a62c","tid":1537432,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e911510d2c358242542ed255493c2021c7eed0e","tid":1537432,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3PY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=0a1e7838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3a11004a26a37f18b6d0aa920349f4cc88c38a","tid":1537432,"uid":69112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db87777b9593b0851aa610fa21ab92acd0458bf0","tid":1537432,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要推"},{"pid":"ec39a21077e8ed7f7d60bd11570609482032eeda","tid":1537432,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會有英字版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbcd99de1b44d96d739f7a006892f53afd9c0f6","tid":1537432,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ae50ed14f2953d34fedbd3a535981dd13f3e1dd","tid":1537432,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"841bdf0aa779829eac7ef02ba66375262fe7ddcc","tid":1537432,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bf4d38ed7f3a65c913